Class ComponentProcessor.Parameter

java.lang.Object

Enclosing class:
ComponentProcessor
protected final class ComponentProcessor.Parameter
extends Object

Represents a parameter consisting of a name and a type. The type is a String representation of the java type, such as "int", "double", or "java.lang.String".

Method Detail

parameterToYailType

protected String parameterToYailType(ComponentProcessor.Parameter parameter)
Provides a Yail type for a given parameter type. This is useful because the parameter types used for ComponentProcessor.Event are Simple types (e.g., "Single"), while the parameter types used for ComponentProcessor.Method are Java types (e.g., "int".

Parameters:
parameter - a parameter
Returns:
the string representation of the corresponding Yail type
Throws:
RuntimeException - if parameter does not have a corresponding Yail type
